2011-09-26T10:27:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/austria-s-fekter-says-greek-haircut-is-last-option-apa-says.html
Austrian Finance Minister Maria
Fekter said a Greek debt restructuring is only “the very last
option” and that she’s certain  Austria ’s parliament will
approve the expansion of the European Financial Stability
Facility, according to the Austrian Press Agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
